branchCategory.name: C(D)QSW, Compact Cylinder, Double Acting, Double Rod
branchCategory.description: <p>The CQS double rod, double acting version of the compact cylinder is available for those small bore cylinder applications where saving space is a concern. The CQS offers strokes up to 50mm. Both switch capable and non-switch capable body styles are the same, and switches can be mounted on three (12-16 bore) and four (20-25 bore) sides.</p>
